name: dash-dual-listbox
description: Dual listbox for Dash. Original component: https://rawgit.com/jyotirmaybanerjee/react-duallist/master/example/examples.html#

scripts.build:py: node ./extract-meta src/lib/components > dash_dual_listbox/metadata.json && copyfiles package.json dash_dual_listbox && python -c "import dash; dash.development.component_loader.generate_classes('dash_dual_listbox', 'dash_dual_listbox/metadata.json')"
scripts.build:all: npm run build:js & npm run build:py
scripts.build:all-dev: npm run build:js-dev & npm run build:py
